{
  "texts": [
    "In our prompt strategy, we have not specifically emphasized medical answers, aiming to mirror normal usage and ensure a fair comparison with the Google search engine.",
    "The assessment of clinical accuracy was based on a straightforward 5-point Likert scale for all three tasks.",
    "While this approach facilitates a standardized comprehension of assessment among different physicians and different clinical disciplines, it is still a subjective instrument.",
    "Different clinical dimensions of accuracy (e.g.",
    "quality of life, surrogate parameters, life expectancy, overall patient safety or harm) were not considered separately and will require further research with multi-dimensional rating scales."
  ]
}